root: ^Tsk, even surviving of all of that, there is still no treasure here.
^Heya Dross, I see you made it out alive.
^Honestly it’s pretty surprising to see you actually make it in one piece.
^Did you manage to find any treasure?
^Not thanks in part due to your help…
^Oh golly, when you put it like that.
^I’m glad I could be of assistance to you.
^So is this the way to the Coral Reef?
^It should be smooth sailing from here on out for you.
^Hope so, I really don’t want to deal with anymore sea folk.
^Well it was a pleasure meeting you little Hermit Crab.
^I’m gonna head back to the surface for a livestream now.
^If you ever feel like coming up there, be sure to drop by.
^I’ll make sure to give you a shout out if you’re there.
^Well take care now you hear, and don’t get accidentally eaten by crazy fish you hear!
^[you see her swim off towards the surface relatively fast]
^Well… that sure was quite the experience.
^The Coral Reef is this way right?
